  "text": [
    "me and you be sisters.",
    "we be the same.",
    "me and you",
    "coming from the same place.",
    "me and you",
    "be greasing our legs",
    "touching up our edges.",
    "me and you",
    "be scared of rats",
    "be stepping on roaches.",
    "me and you",
    "come running high down purdy street one time",
    "and mama laugh and shake her head at",
    "me and you.",
    "me and you",
    "got babies",
    "got thirty-five",
    "got black",
    "let our hair go back",
    "be loving ourselves",
    "be loving ourselves",
    "be sisters.",
    "only where you sing",
    "i poet."
  ],
  "title": "sisters",
